{"tid":198334,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［絞盡腦汁］結合mastermind 同 android 既解鎖遊戲","createTime":"2017-04-12T12:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T00:52:52.000Z","uid":18641,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0974648cb0cb86b9021f25bbdb65553d4a4751b","tid":198334,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:17:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://maxwellito.github.io/breaklock/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaxwellito.github.io%2Fbreaklock%2F&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8tibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=6fe2de99\" target=\"_blank\">https://maxwellito.github.io/breaklock/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A37RzUZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA37RzUZ.jpg&h=6e9066b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係一隻結合咗mastermind 同 android pattern lock 既解鎖遊戲，有玩過mastermind 既人應該好快就可以上手，未玩過既可以趁呢個機會學下點玩。<br />\n<br />\n玩法就係你每試一個組合，電腦都會根據你既組合回饋返一啲資訊比你去估返個答案係咩。每個空心代表你個組合入面有一點既位置係啱咗，而每個實心就代表你個組合入面一點既位置同次序係同時啱咗。<br />\n<br />\n而呢隻game同mastermind唔同既地方係佢有唔同既難度同模式，最難既係去到估六個點既pattern<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  平時既mastermind 都係4個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自問聰明伶俐既你可以挑戰下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個係開發者既網站<a href=\"https://github.com/maxwellito\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fmaxwellito&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8tibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=0dbdbaa4\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/maxwellito</a>"},{"pid":"970664922a8cc5919df40dd439491fc4953fb469","tid":198334,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58470d2f2e78602408ed0ceddbf815f7fd084dec","tid":198334,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9c2f527472e0585c65f59cf157838e33be17ef","tid":198334,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90b962aff75886604975ef18b609dba5b85688f","tid":198334,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d04b94eaf1a351919cd8e36f45b46485bca9ea1","tid":198334,"uid":29655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/203211_7c70813a01920ca838a7971fc33bf463.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F203211_7c70813a01920ca838a7971fc33bf463.jpg&h=eef00e96&s={SIZE}\" />都幾難玩 估得中4點仲要估次序就好難"},{"pid":"a19a4f3d00001662e83c2335f579786983bde83e","tid":198334,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:37:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/203211_7c70813a01920ca838a7971fc33bf463.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F203211_7c70813a01920ca838a7971fc33bf463.jpg&h=eef00e96&s={SIZE}\" />都幾難玩 估得中4點仲要估次序就好難</blockquote><br />\n加油,玩多啲就會知道點樣有效地用邏輯推理返個答案出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個遊戲用嚟訓練邏輯思維一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7695c4489c982f009024938ed70f6ca9a76685f","tid":198334,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/204231_bb391606f6268fd44ed75557b17efda2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F204231_bb391606f6268fd44ed75557b17efda2.jpg&h=04ae1f04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人一齊拆解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8478f3c53ea08a03ec59620785b005581ed5bb74","tid":198334,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50961664f0311c2ab65e93143d83050e3e1ff1a4","tid":198334,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:09:27.000Z","msg":"召集連登所有頭腦一齊拆解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n或者討論下策略"},{"pid":"bfd70a6d12f2fc2425908800f4ad03d8123a73fa","tid":198334,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:20:17.000Z","msg":"有無人係玩緊架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8025789274cb3f978c2ca0372d2e9ca97bf40aa","tid":198334,"uid":1095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:30:44.000Z","msg":"好難 <br />\n51 attempts 先完成一個"},{"pid":"ab72fe856836e08bf62a7563412b194f5deeed37","tid":198334,"uid":59964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:47:27.000Z","msg":"用小畫家易玩好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34849cfa5e4da73780744aa14ef958a56b6543aa","tid":198334,"uid":1644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:49:46.000Z","msg":"好難玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩緊easy 既practice<br />\n諗住練下個思維先<br />\n最長試過18次先得 最快5次<br />\n<br />\n成日連連下就亂左 唔記得之前d 假設<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就黎要用筆寫低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但癮已上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f3dedb51c75605f4fa56b30252a4fb79773f98","tid":198334,"uid":1644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/204231_bb391606f6268fd44ed75557b17efda2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F204231_bb391606f6268fd44ed75557b17efda2.jpg&h=04ae1f04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人一齊拆解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n6粒真係睇都唔想睇sosad"},{"pid":"69471f2db7a85d7f04e524540e0cc40c554c2a12","tid":198334,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:59:36.000Z","msg":"空心實心圓係咪同畫嘅次序無關係？"},{"pid":"80a50279cca3b4f6a7888a597ef64f3d2dfe00b1","tid":198334,"uid":1644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:03:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>空心實心圓係咪同畫嘅次序無關係？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n空心=位置岩次序錯<br />\n實心=次序同位置都岩"},{"pid":"9c46a813df290d4ac7e2578f5cf63f24eb7e1ca7","tid":198334,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:05:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>空心實心圓係咪同畫嘅次序無關係？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n空心=位置岩次序錯<br />\n實心=次序同位置都岩</blockquote><br />\n呢個我知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我另外以為實心第一粒= step 1 exactly中 原來唔係"},{"pid":"3f81eccd1edf48c9fbbe593bca8f27030b2fbfa6","tid":198334,"uid":1644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:20:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>空心實心圓係咪同畫嘅次序無關係？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n空心=位置岩次序錯<br />\n實心=次序同位置都岩</blockquote><br />\n呢個我知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我另外以為實心第一粒= step 1 exactly中 原來唔係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咁易就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d1e58916e66564824aa35d220345cbbe2ffa9b","tid":198334,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:20:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>空心實心圓係咪同畫嘅次序無關係？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n空心=位置岩次序錯<br />\n實心=次序同位置都岩</blockquote><br />\n呢個我知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我另外以為實心第一粒= step 1 exactly中 原來唔係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咁易就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但真係好撚好玩 <br />\n10 attempts 5 dots<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a78e93489c4028a973d24415e51a141c6fc602","tid":198334,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>空心實心圓係咪同畫嘅次序無關係？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n空心=位置岩次序錯<br />\n實心=次序同位置都岩</blockquote><br />\n呢個我知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我另外以為實心第一粒= step 1 exactly中 原來唔係</blockquote><br />\n佢可以係你組合入面任何一粒，所以要諗好多個組合<br />\n<br />\n但係你可從已有資訊排除某啲組合而收窄個答案既可能組合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88db9bef70fb33ebf3ceec5069bfaac9adc4ccb4","tid":198334,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:23:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>空心實心圓係咪同畫嘅次序無關係？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n空心=位置岩次序錯<br />\n實心=次序同位置都岩</blockquote><br />\n呢個我知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我另外以為實心第一粒= step 1 exactly中 原來唔係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咁易就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但真係好撚好玩 <br />\n10 attempts 5 dots<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打可以試下6粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f8e672ee0597e008eb1084275be7da8e931905","tid":198334,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:35:41.000Z","msg":"有好多野要做，但係又好想玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c08fb849f308065576f0b590d8e7d28f7ee5d5","tid":198334,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s2i9F7m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs2i9F7m.jpg&h=d05336b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人一齊傾下點拆解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101ef988963191570cda5541b5473453e4ef7fc4","tid":198334,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:39:38.000Z","msg":"連登有無高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}